description: The Sweet and Mellow truck serves up the ‘best of the best’ from independent small batch roasters and artisan bakers. We source locally whenever possible.  Our Specialty coffee house on wheels is a fun and unique place for you and your friends to enjoy.  Whether it’s at community events, company functions,  private catered parties or wherever you happen to be, we’ll transport you to a very Sweet and Mellow place.
name: Sweet and Mellow
